{"word":"περιφανής","slug":"περιφανής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περιφανής</b></el> <el>(περιφᾰνής, ές) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:περιφαίνομαι'><el>περιφαίνομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>seen all round</i>, of a city, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>conspicuous, manifest, notable, notorious</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> and <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a>, <el>-φανέστερος, -έστατος</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-νῶς</el>, <i>conspicuously, notably, manifestly</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>-έστερον</el>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}